---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-24 pt-10 pb-12 border-t rule">
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between gap-6">
    <div class="max-w-md">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-3">Colophon</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-400 leading-relaxed">
        A site by Erik Smith. Built with Astro and Tailwind. Set in
        <span class="font-display text-ink-200">Fraunces</span>,
        <span class="font-sans text-ink-200">Geist</span>, and
        <span class="font-mono text-ink-200">JetBrains Mono</span>.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-6 font-mono text-sm text-ink-500">
      <a href="https://github.com/provandal" class="hover:text-signal transition-colors">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://x.com/provandal" class="hover:text-signal transition-colors">X</a>
      <a href="/rss.xml" class="hover:text-signal transition-colors">RSS</a>
      <span class="text-ink-700">·</span>
      <span>&copy; {year}</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
